<strong>Using the Internet, you can find limitless information on limitless topics.</strong></p class="lead">
								<hr>		
	
								<p>The information you find will be in many forms - text, pictures, graphics, audio, video, interactive and combinations of these.</p>
								<p>So, how can you find all of this information? Some of the most commonly used ways to search the Internet are by using <strong>search engines</strong> and <strong>meta search engines</strong>. Let's learn more about them.</p>
							</div>
